{"tid":2209103,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈旭暉 :拜登家族的中國金主：何志平足以改變選舉結果？","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T04:39:27.000Z","uid":282637,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8b54ec09afccb6238892f7cc4f13d532c713a8","tid":2209103,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"【萬國時空．沈旭暉 021🇺🇸】拜登家族的中國金主：何志平足以改變選舉結果？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9a6Lg8kLCVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9a6Lg8kLCVQ&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=0e340dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9a6Lg8kLCVQ</a><br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n<br />\n美國總統民主黨候選人拜登的兒子Hunter Biden，與中國關係撲朔迷離。他的顧問公司「專長」，就是「聯繫」第三世界政要，這正是何志平在白手套基金會的秘書長「工作」，二人一拍即合。這基金會年來不斷舉行半官方會議，邀請中美雙方的軍人在香港見面，在美方穿針引線的人，不會有很多選擇。後來基金會金主葉簡明事敗，何志平因為賄賂非洲政要被捕，基金會副秘書長路祥安時間巧合地「暴斃身亡」，火藥沒有朝（在美國同樣有任務在身的）董建華方向引爆，卻成了Hunter Biden的死穴。何志平被捕時，第一時間居然是打電話給拜登弟弟James Biden求救-- 對，不是Hunter，而是拜登的弟弟James。James對法庭說，何志平搞錯了，他只是要致電Hunter，自己「完全無辜」。但拜登家族，沒有一個是蘑菇的......<br />\n<br />\n⏺ 拜登的致命傷：何志平・夜總會兄弟・新疆<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/41137446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F41137446&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=61e6f0a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/41137446</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"be792605ab748e12fb7cd10a00f38284d94efd4d","tid":2209103,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5771d9cb7be303fd3fdc39fb04f10b6f360eef70","tid":2209103,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e88e33a359588420cf45b20fd2e127e49c3e32e","tid":2209103,"uid":78492,